sub_title: Quantum Delta Netherlands, co-founder & director of ecosystem development
summary: Building the European quantum ecosystem with the ambition to contribute to a more peaceful and sustainable world. Co-chair of World Economic Forum Global Future Council on Quantum Computing. Experienced Innovation Director with a history of policy management in national government and public-private ecosystems. Passionate innovator with strong program management skills and a leading voice in international arenas. Professionally skilled in Systems Engineering, ICT, International Relations, Economic policy, People Management.
